      "body" : "Can you post what <code>-Dprism.verbose=&quot;true&quot;</code> gives you? On Windows, I&#39;ve noticed that with <code>-Dprism.allowhidpi=&quot;false&quot;</code> I get <code>Not opting in for HiDPI pixel scaling</code>, while <code>-Dprism.allowhidpi=&quot;true&quot;</code> gives <code>Opting in for HiDPI pixel scaling</code>."
