    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This worked in Ubuntu Gnome: <code>-Dglass.gtk.uiScale=4.0</code></p>\n<p>It made GUI 4x bigger.</p>\n<p>More detailed answer: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/79832355/20340543\">https://stackoverflow.com/a/79832355/20340543</a></p>\n"
  } ],
