  "title" : "Force JavaFX Hi-DPI mode to be enabled",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a way to \"force\" JavaFX to enable the Hi-DPI mode? Maybe through some specific VM-argument or something? This would be highly useful for debugging/testing an application without having access to a respective display.</p>\n\n<p>This question already covers the basics about JavaFX 8's Hi-DPI mode pretty well, but it doesn't give any way of \"enforcing\" the mode to be active: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26182460/javafx-8-hidpi-support/26184471?s=4|0.3364#26184471\">JavaFX 8 HiDPI Support</a></p>\n"
